<h2 id="discord">Discord</h2>
<p>The fastest way to ask a question or get help is to join our Pi Ecosystem Discord Server. In this server you will find many other developers who are also building on Pi and can assist you with any questions. The Core Team is active in that server as well and can assist.</p>

<h2 id="pi-app-chat">Pi App Chat</h2>
